Package com.ansi.scilla.common.jobticket

Class TicketDateGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ansi.scilla.common.ApplicationObject
      • com.ansi.scilla.common.jobticket.TicketDateGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class TicketDateGenerator
extends ApplicationObject
    Each method in this object should match up with a value in the JobFrequence enum, and returns a list of dates for which a ticket should be generated to match the job frequence, start date, and run time.
    Author:
    ggroce
